resources.string: The world largest technical professional organization for the advancement of technology
IEEE Student Branch falls under IEEE Bombay Section, a technical network of doctoral, masters, and undergraduate students of ABV-IIITM Gwalior, was established on April 12,2019.
This association enables students to utilize the benefits of IEEE membership, including scholarships, competitions, and conference grants.
Aims to organize social and technical activities that promotes sharing of knowledge in science, technology, and engineering.
IEEE Student Branch becomes an intermidiate for students to be a part of the global IEEE community and share their ideas with IEEE brances all over the world.
